#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:1
msgid "Args API"
msgstr "Args API"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:3
msgid "CLI argument schema and parsing helpers are available under `ptool.args` and `p.args`."
msgstr "CLI 参数模式定义与解析辅助能力位于 `ptool.args` 和 `p.args` 下。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:5
msgid "ptool.args.arg"
msgstr "ptool.args.arg"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:7
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:7"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:9
msgid "`ptool.args.arg(id, kind, options)` creates an argument builder for use in `ptool.args.parse(...).schema.args`."
msgstr "`ptool.args.arg(id, kind, options)` 创建一个参数构造器，用于 `ptool.args.parse(...).schema.args`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:12
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:12"
msgid "`id` (string, required): The argument identifier. It is also the key in the returned table."
msgstr "`id`（string，必填）：参数标识符。它也会作为返回表中的键。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:14
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:14"
msgid "`kind` (string, required): The argument type. Supported values:"
msgstr "`kind`（string，必填）：参数类型。支持："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:14
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:14"
msgid "`\"flag\"`: A boolean flag."
msgstr "`\"flag\"`：布尔开关。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:14
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:14"
msgid "`\"string\"`: A string option."
msgstr "`\"string\"`：字符串选项。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:14
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:14"
msgid "`\"int\"`: An integer option (`i64`)."
msgstr "`\"int\"`：整数选项（`i64`）。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:14
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:14"
msgid "`\"positional\"`: A positional argument."
msgstr "`\"positional\"`：位置参数。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:19
msgid "`options` (table, optional): The same optional fields supported by argument tables in `ptool.args.parse`, such as `long`, `short`, `help`, `required`, `multiple`, and `default`."
msgstr "`options`（table，可选）：与 `ptool.args.parse` 中参数表支持的可选字段相同， 例如 `long`、`short`、`help`、`required`、`multiple` 和 `default`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:23
msgid "The builder supports chainable methods, all of which return itself:"
msgstr "构造器支持链式方法，且每个方法都会返回自身："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:25
msgid "`arg:long(value)` sets the long option name. Supported only for non-`positional` arguments."
msgstr "`arg:long(value)`：设置长选项名。仅适用于非 `positional` 参数。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:27
msgid "`arg:short(value)` sets the short option name. Supported only for non-`positional` arguments."
msgstr "`arg:short(value)`：设置短选项名。仅适用于非 `positional` 参数。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:29
msgid "`arg:help(value)` sets the help text."
msgstr "`arg:help(value)`：设置帮助文本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:30
msgid "`arg:required(value)` sets whether the argument is required. If `value` is omitted, it defaults to `true`."
msgstr "`arg:required(value)`：设置参数是否必填。如果省略 `value`，默认是 `true`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:32
msgid "`arg:multiple(value)` sets whether the argument can be repeated. If `value` is omitted, it defaults to `true`."
msgstr "`arg:multiple(value)`：设置参数是否可重复。如果省略 `value`，默认是 `true`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:34
msgid "`arg:default(value)` sets the default value. If `value = nil`, the default is cleared."
msgstr "`arg:default(value)`：设置默认值。如果 `value = nil`，则清除默认值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:37
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

