msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:51
msgid "`v0.3.0` - Added `subcommands` support."
msgstr "`v0.3.0` - 添加 `subcommands` 支持。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:55
msgid "`ptool.args.parse(schema)` parses script arguments with `clap` and returns a table indexed by `id`."
msgstr "`ptool.args.parse(schema)` 使用 `clap` 解析脚本参数，并返回一个以 `id` 为键的表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:58
msgid "Script arguments come from the part after `--` in `ptool run <lua_file> -- ...`."
msgstr "脚本参数来自 `ptool run <lua_file> -- ...` 中 `--` 之后的部分。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:60
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:60"
msgid "For example:"
msgstr "例如："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:76
msgid "Schema Structure"
msgstr "Schema 结构"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:78
msgid "`name` (string, optional): The command name, used in help output. Defaults to the script file name."
msgstr "`name`（string，可选）：命令名称，用于帮助输出。默认是脚本文件名。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:80
msgid "`about` (string, optional): Help description."
msgstr "`about`（string，可选）：帮助描述。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:81
msgid "`args` (table, optional): An array of argument definitions. Each item supports two forms:"
msgstr "`args`（table，可选）：参数定义数组。每个元素支持两种形式："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:81
msgid "An argument table."
msgstr "参数表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:81
msgid "A builder object returned by `ptool.args.arg(...)`."
msgstr "`ptool.args.arg(...)` 返回的构造器对象。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:85
msgid "`subcommands` (table, optional): A map of subcommand name to subcommand schema. Each subcommand schema supports `about`, `args`, and `subcommands` recursively."
msgstr "`subcommands`（table，可选）：子命令名到子命令 schema 的映射。每个子命令 schema 都支持递归定义 `about`、`args` 和 `subcommands`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:89
msgid "At least one of `args` or `subcommands` must be provided."
msgstr "`args` 和 `subcommands` 至少要提供一个。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:91
msgid "Argument table fields:"
msgstr "参数表字段："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:93
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:93"
msgid "`id` (string, required): The argument identifier. It is also the key in the returned table."
msgstr "`id`（string，必填）：参数标识符。它也会作为返回表中的键。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:95
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:95"
msgid "`kind` (string, required): The argument type. Supported values:"
msgstr "`kind`（string，必填）：参数类型。支持："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:95
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:95"
msgid "`\"flag\"`: A boolean flag."
msgstr "`\"flag\"`：布尔开关。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:95
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:95"
msgid "`\"string\"`: A string option."
msgstr "`\"string\"`：字符串选项。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:95
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:95"
msgid "`\"int\"`: An integer option (`i64`)."
msgstr "`\"int\"`：整数选项（`i64`）。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:95
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:95"
msgid "`\"positional\"`: A positional argument."
msgstr "`\"positional\"`：位置参数。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:100
msgid "`long` (string, optional): The long option name, such as `\"name\"` for `--name`. For non-`positional` arguments, the default can be derived from `id`."
msgstr "`long`（string，可选）：长选项名，例如 `\"name\"` 对应 `--name`。对于非 `positional` 参数，默认可以从 `id` 推导。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:103
msgid "`short` (string, optional): The short option name, a single character such as `\"v\"` for `-v`."
msgstr "`short`（string，可选）：短选项名，单个字符，例如 `\"v\"` 对应 `-v`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:105
msgid "`help` (string, optional): Help text for the argument."
msgstr "`help`（string，可选）：参数帮助文本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:106
msgid "`required` (boolean, optional): Whether the argument is required. Defaults to `false`."
msgstr "`required`（boolean，可选）：参数是否必填。默认是 `false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:108
msgid "`multiple` (boolean, optional): Whether the argument can be repeated. Defaults to `false`."
msgstr "`multiple`（boolean，可选）：参数是否允许重复出现。默认是 `false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:110
msgid "`default` (string/integer, optional): The default value."
msgstr "`default`（string/integer，可选）：默认值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:112
msgid "When `subcommands` is present, the current command's `args` act as shared options for that command tree, and are accepted before or after the selected subcommand."
msgstr "当存在 `subcommands` 时，当前命令层级里的 `args` 会作为该命令树的共享选项， 可以写在所选子命令之前，也可以写在之后。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:116
msgid "Example with subcommands:"
msgstr "带子命令的示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:147
msgid "Constraints"
msgstr "约束"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:149
msgid "The following constraints apply to both argument tables and builder syntax."
msgstr "下列约束同时适用于参数表形式和构造器语法。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:150
msgid "Non-`positional` arguments may omit `long` and `short`. If `long` is omitted, `id` is used automatically."
msgstr "非 `positional` 参数可以省略 `long` 和 `short`。如果省略 `long`，会自动使用 `id`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:152
msgid "`positional` arguments cannot set `long`, `short`, or `default`."
msgstr "`positional` 参数不能设置 `long`、`short` 或 `default`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:153
msgid "When `positional.multiple = true`, it must be the last argument in `args`."
msgstr "当 `positional.multiple = true` 时，它必须是 `args` 中最后一个参数。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:154
msgid "`multiple = true` is supported only for `string` and `positional`."
msgstr "`multiple = true` 只支持 `string` 和 `positional`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:155
msgid "`default` is supported only for `string` and `int`, and cannot be used together with `multiple = true`."
msgstr "`default` 只支持 `string` 和 `int`，且不能与 `multiple = true` 同时使用。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:157
msgid "When `subcommands` is present, `positional` arguments are not allowed in that same schema."
msgstr "当存在 `subcommands` 时，同一层 schema 中不能定义 `positional` 参数。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:159
msgid "When `subcommands` is present at the top level, argument ids `command_path` and `args` are reserved."
msgstr "当顶层存在 `subcommands` 时，参数 id `command_path` 和 `args` 为保留名。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:161
msgid "Along one selected subcommand path, ancestor and descendant subcommands cannot reuse the same argument `id`, because their values are merged into one `args` table."
msgstr "在一条实际命中的子命令路径上，祖先和后代子命令不能复用同一个参数 `id`， 因为它们会被合并到同一个 `args` 表里。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:165
msgid "Return Value"
msgstr "返回值"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:167
msgid "A Lua table is returned where keys are `id` and value types are as follows:"
msgstr "返回一个 Lua 表，其中键为 `id`，值类型如下："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:169
msgid "`flag` -> `boolean`"
msgstr "`flag` -> `boolean`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:170
msgid "`string` -> `string` (or `string[]` when `multiple = true`)"
msgstr "`string` -> `string`（当 `multiple = true` 时为 `string[]`）"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:171
msgid "`int` -> `integer`"
msgstr "`int` -> `integer`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:172
msgid "`positional` -> `string` (or `string[]` when `multiple = true`)"
msgstr "`positional` -> `string`（当 `multiple = true` 时为 `string[]`）"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:174
msgid "When `subcommands` is not present, the return value stays flat as above."
msgstr "当不存在 `subcommands` 时，返回结构保持上述扁平形式不变。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:176
msgid "When `subcommands` is present, the return value has this shape:"
msgstr "当存在 `subcommands` 时，返回结构如下："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:178
msgid "Top-level `args` values are returned directly on the top-level table."
msgstr "顶层 `args` 的值直接放在顶层表上。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:179
msgid "`command_path` -> `string[]`: The matched subcommand path, for example `{\"build\", \"web\"}`."
msgstr "`command_path` -> `string[]`：命中的子命令路径，例如 `{\"build\", \"web\"}`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:181
msgid "`args` -> `table`: The merged argument values from the matched subcommand path."
msgstr "`args` -> `table`：命中的子命令路径上所有参数合并后的结果表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:183
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/args.md:183"
msgid "For example:"
msgstr "例如："
